Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.97,0:02:07.98,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,472)}{\fad(500,0)\fscy120\blur4\bord0\1c&H000000}三年四班 Ⅲ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.73,0:02:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早安 艾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.57,0:02:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}蒂伊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.24,0:02:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我已經決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.41,0:02:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我要把一切都告訴艾利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.16,0:02:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不論是輪迴的起因 還是我已死的事實
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.59,0:02:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我在那之後想了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.09,0:02:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}最後終於下定了決心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.64,0:02:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾 謝謝你一直替我隱瞞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.68,0:02:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可是…那樣…蒂伊你…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.40,0:02:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}已經不要緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.15,0:02:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我剛才也跟艾利斯說了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.15,0:03:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}說有事情要告訴他 叫他過來一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.41,0:03:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你能答應我一個請求嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.12,0:03:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可以
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我希望艾你也能來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}蒂伊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.92,0:03:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我希望在告訴艾利斯實情的時候有艾在身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.35,0:03:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.15,0:03:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你在後院那個籃球場裡等我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.32,0:03:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我馬上就過去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.13,0:03:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼了 你也被叫來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.55,0:03:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.80,0:04:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她到底要說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.01,0:04:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我都叫她不要賣關子了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.39,0:04:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可她就是不說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.81,0:04:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她是想鄭重地跟你說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.44,0:04:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是不是知道些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.69,0:04:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼了 是跟輪迴有關的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.86,0:04:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這個…我不能說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.32,0:04:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.20,0:04:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以…就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.54,0:04:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你還是聽蒂伊親口說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.30,0:04:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}各位早安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.10,0:04:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是你啊 來得真晚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.43,0:04:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}話說 艾利斯和艾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.98,0:04:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒有跟你在一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.27,0:05:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.53,0:05:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}蒂伊?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.28,0:05:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}門希姆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.83,0:05:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.14,0:05:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你…你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.72,0:05:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好好看清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.64,0:05:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.02,0:05:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}奇怪 我怎麼睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.65,0:05:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.03,0:05:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.82,0:05:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家都怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.74,0:05:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.12,0:05:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是怎麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.13,0:06:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你看 這很荒誕吧 很莫名其妙吧 很不可思議吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.68,0:06:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我會把一切…把一切都告訴你們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.52,0:06:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家其實都已經知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.02,0:06:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只是忘記了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.73,0:06:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.61,0:06:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我就讓你們想起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.57,0:06:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}蒂伊好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.16,0:06:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}昨天謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.95,0:06:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝你聽我發牢騷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.92,0:06:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你真是個不可思議的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.50,0:06:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我還是第一次碰到像你這樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.47,0:06:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還有在生日那天我也被你折服了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.72,0:06:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我真軟弱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.43,0:06:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼在你面前我就會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.19,0:07:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為何唯獨在你面前會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.61,0:07:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請不要說唯獨在我面前什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.82,0:07:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}心裡有什麼想法對大家說出來就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.12,0:07:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家一定會傾聽的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.37,0:07:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你真是個不可思議的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.00,0:07:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼樣 想起來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.88,0:07:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}快想起來了吧 已經想起來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.88,0:07:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.01,0:07:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對 就在那時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.15,0:07:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.02,0:07:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那時候我們無論如何也不能接受
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.20,0:07:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}無法相信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.66,0:07:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}流了好多好多的血
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.87,0:07:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.04,0:07:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.95,0:08:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不願相信那是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.87,0:08:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真希望那是騙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.38,0:08:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.50,0:08:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們就許願了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.26,0:08:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們在那時候…在那天傍晚許願了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.68,0:08:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們看著樓下的屍體許願了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.64,0:08:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這不是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.10,0:08:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們不要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.69,0:08:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請讓這一切從未發生過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.11,0:08:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請把原本那快樂的生活還給我們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.36,0:08:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請讓這快樂的生活永遠持續下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.16,0:08:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果那時許下的願望是讓死者復活那該多好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.00,0:08:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.04,0:08:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那時候大家一同祈求永恆了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.55,0:08:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想必現在也是這麼希望的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.51,0:08:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可是你們都想起來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.43,0:08:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想重來一次是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.60,0:08:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想再忘記一次是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.52,0:09:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對於那天的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.44,0:09:13.94,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\1c&H4C4C4C&\fs90\frz332\frx10\fry342\org(832,226)\pos(1044,278)\blur3}7月28日
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.40,0:09:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.32,0:09:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們再重新開始一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.82,0:09:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}從頭開始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.66,0:09:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎…怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.58,0:09:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是蒂伊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.95,0:09:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她要重設整個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.80,0:09:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.02,0:09:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她肯定是解除了四班全體同學的記憶限制
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.81,0:09:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}空間已經承受不住矛盾了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.41,0:10:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我說…這牌匾上的字是不是寫錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.75,0:10:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊…是真的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.59,0:10:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是誰寫的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.71,0:10:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我忘記拿收據了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.84,0:10:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}班長就不能想想辦法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.06,0:10:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}自…自掏腰包
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.82,0:10:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我要重設這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.45,0:10:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}包括我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.09,0:10:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}疤面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.09,0:10:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.30,0:10:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}尤力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.64,0:11:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.56,0:11:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}城鎮被湮沒在煙霧中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.73,0:11:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這就是他說的重設嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.19,0:11:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.90,0:11:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.74,0:11:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對我而言這是第一次被重設啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.08,0:11:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}整整十四年的回憶即將要消失了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.46,0:11:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}無論是與艾利斯共度的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.01,0:11:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還是艾利斯那隻對我展現過的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.35,0:11:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但這一幕一定要重演
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.47,0:11:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我要和那時一樣掉下來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.85,0:11:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}和那時一樣死去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.10,0:11:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}重重地摔在地面上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.03,0:12:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}遭受到讓我甚至無法作為死人活過來的嚴重傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.90,0:12:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.26,0:13:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}煙霧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.93,0:13:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}正逐漸消散
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.56,0:13:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我終於明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.15,0:13:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}死去的不是蒂伊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.57,0:13:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而是艾利斯是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.57,0:13:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}正確
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.12,0:13:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那時我為了救蒂伊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.08,0:13:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}結果讓自己掉了下去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.29,0:13:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}掉下去
