Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.86,0:14:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你不想讓自己消失
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.65,0:14:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以才一直妨礙我…
