Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.13,0:14:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你不會消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.34,0:14:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以盡可放心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.96,0:14:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}回到外面的世界去吧
