Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.83,0:15:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好 你們都回到外面的世界去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.71,0:15:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}回到外面去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.92,0:15:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}長到17歲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.13,0:15:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}然後長到18歲 再長到19歲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.63,0:15:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}每年都迎來自己的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.76,0:15:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}然後逐漸長成大人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.76,0:15:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.23,0:16:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就算變成大人了也要記住我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.65,0:16:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要忘記我
